name: Bright Babushka Earrings
description:
Unique and Fun.

Each babushka/matryoshka doll is unique with her own beautiful bright attire, so you will get an individual pair with each purchase! 

These earrings would make a lovely gift for someone special - perhaps a 'Babushka' or 'Matryoshka' figure in your life? 

Size:13x18 mm

Materials:  Resin and silver plated base and earring hook.

name: Three Peas in a Pod Earrings - Dark Green
description:
Quirky and Fun.

Three little peas in a pod. These earrings remind me of the special bonds that are shared between people.

Silver wire wrapped and attached to silver earring hooks, they are elegant and striking.

Size: Earring pendant is approximately 30mm, glass beads 6mm

Customer comments:
"Hi Sophie. I got my earrings today - I love them. Thankyou, thankyou, thankyou :)" - Mandy.

"Thank you for the beautiful pod earrings which arrived last week - can't wait to give them to my girlfriend for her birthday." - Pip

name: White Doily with Clear Glass Bead Earrings
description:
Elegant with a vintage twist.

These 'doily' filigree earrings are a beautiful, ornate design, embellished with a 6mm glass bead. 

Add a little bit of vintage style to your wardrobe this season!

Size: 40mm x 45mm pendant, 6mm bead

name: Bright Green Filigree Earrings
description:
Bright and Intricate!

These beautiful filigree earrings are back by popular demand! A gorgeous and brightly painted filigree pendant which warms up your wardrobe. 

Embellished with three beautiful beads which catch the light and show off a bright personality.

Size: 58 x 48 mm

Material: The base metal is a silver plated brass, painted. 
6mm clear glass bead, 4mm green glass bead and a tiny 2mm green glass bead to really catch the light. 
Adorned with gunmetal earring hooks.

Customer comments:
"So many comments on them, Sophie!! xx" - Christie.

name: Felted Acorn Brooch
description:
This gorgeous, little, lonesome acorn could sure do with a home!

A lovely, elegant addition to your coat or shirt this season. The handmade wool felted acorn hangs delicately from a vintage safety pin brooch.

Available in a range of colours.

name: Summer Branch Earrings
description:
Intricate and elegant.

This beautiful pair of gold plated branches, embellished with czech glass beads will add an intricate element to your attire.

Slipping seamlessly from work wear to evening wear, they are suitably elegant for a range of occasions.

name: Mustard Doily with Glass Bead Earrings
description:
Bright and fun with a vintage twist.

These 'doily' filigree earrings are a beautiful, ornate design, embellished with two yellow, glass 4mm beads. 
Mustard is the new black and will add a little bit of fun and colour to your wardrobe this season!

Size: 40mm x 45mm pendant, 4mm beads

name: Blue Mrs Pots Earrings
description:
Fun and Quirky.

With these bright and quirky earrings morning tea is never far away! 

These polka dot lampwork beads are set off by a silver tea pot and add character to your attire.

These are a unique, fun earring for the lover of tea (or beauty and the beast for that matter!).

My Mrs. Pots Earrings have been featured on "The Hoopla" an online news and magazine site for a community of wise, warm, witty and wonderful women.
Also available in blue and white!

Materials: Tibetan Silver, 10mm hand painted polka dot Indian lampwork bead.

name: Mrs. Pots Earrings
description:
Fun and Quirky.

With these bright and quirky earrings morning tea is never far away! 

These polka dot lampwork beads are set off by a silver tea pot and add character to your attire.

These are a unique, fun earring for the lover of tea (or beauty and the beast for that matter!).

My Mrs. Pots Earrings have been featured on "The Hoopla" an online news and magazine site for a community of wise, warm, witty and wonderful women.
Also available in blue and white!

Materials: Tibetan Silver, 10mm hand painted polka dot Indian lampwork bead.

name: Miniature Babushka Brooch
description:
Gorgeous and Unique.

These three little woodcut Babushka's measure in at approximately 18x28mm x 3mm and line up beautifully on this three tiered wire brooch.

Not only a unique style, but each Babushka is also unique; dressed in a gorgeous, bright patterened outfit.

This brooch is a great way to add some fun to your outfit!

name: Rhodium or Gold Plated Matte Finish Earrings
description:
Intricate and Delicate.

These modern, silver (or gold) , matte finish earrings depict a beautiful intricate design, looped together with a kidney wire earring hook.

The elegant, contemporary design would make a wonderful gift for yourself, or someone special.

Size: Pendant 29mm x 32mm, Kidney earwire 33mm.

name: Bronze Bird and Branch Lariat
description:
Contemporary and Unique.

The bronze plump bird lariat hangs elegantly through a bronze branch charm.

This necklace is held together with a bronze toggle clasp on a bronze figaro long and short chain.

This unique design would make a lovely gift for yourself or someone special.

Size: Bird 15 mm, branch 19 x 40mm

Materials: Antiqued bronze.

name: Black Filigree Leaves
description:
Intricate and Eye Catching.

These gorgeous black filigree earrings are a lovely elegant accessory, depicting the detail of a skeletal leaf. 

With a stark black enamel applied to front and reverse of these earrings they are a beautifully finished and timeless accessory to add to your wardrobe. They would look fantastic with a little black dress and add elegance to work wear.

Measurement:38mm
Material: Enamel black filigree

name: Yellow Polka Dot Earrings
description:
Bright and Fun.

Itsy-bitsy, teeny-weeny, yellow polka dot... earrings!

These bright polka dot earring will awaken your wardrobe. Measuring in at 20mm on a silver plated base and placed on a silver plated kidney wire hook these gorgeous little earrings are also embellished with 4mm yellow beads.

name: Plum Doily with Glass Bead Earrings
description:
Intricate and feminine with a vintage twist.

Add a little nostalgia to your wardrobe today with these elegant earrings which can easily slip from work wear to evening wear.

These 'doily' filigree earrings are a beautiful, ornate design, embellished with a plum 4mm, glass bead. 

Size: 40mm x 45mm pendant, 4mm beads

name: Nesting Eggs Necklace
description:
Treasured and Unique.

This hand weaved nest holds within it three special little eggs. I made a necklace similar to this one for my Mama for Mothers Day; she had for the first time in 25 years had an empty nest. Now she wears her three little 'chickens' around her neck, although we are far apart.

Whether you are nesting or have an empty nest, this little necklace is a beautiful addition to your outfit and would make a beautiful gift for a loved one.

Matrerials: 20 gauge wire non tarnish silver plated, 3 x 6mm Picasso czech beads, rhodium plated twig, silver plated long and short fiagro chain and tubetan silver toggle clasp.

name: Mod Birds Free From Their Cages Earrings
description:
Cute and classy.

These matte finish birds can be seen to be perched delicately in their bronze cages, but I prefer to think of them as breaking free from them!

The deliberate contrast of materials used in these earrings ensures they match a range of outfits and tastes, incorporating both silver and antiqued bronze in their finish. 

Size: Bird 10.5 x 8.5mm, birdcage 24x16mm

Materials: Matte finish Rhodium, antiqued bronze cage and earring hooks

name: Babushka Brooch
description:
Bright and Cute.

Ever since my Mama bought me a gorgeous babushka brooch, I have been unable to resist anything babushka - as you no doubt have already noticed! I hope you are as excited about beautiful babushka's as I am, because you've come to the right place!

This gorgeous babushka brooch comes in two different bright options and is sure to spice up your outfit. It would also make a wonderful gift for someone special who has been a nurturing figure in your life, as this is what it symbolises to me.

Size: 55mm x 35mm x 3mm.

Materials: Wood, hand painted and treated by waterproof, anti-oxidation and scratch-resistant process, Silver plated brooch back.

name: Nesting Bird Ring
description:
Tweet Tweet!

I created this little nesting bird who sits, warming its three little eggs with the idea of mothers looking after their young.

This miniature bronze, plump bird can sit upon your finger in a beautiful wearable art piece.

Size: Adjustable ring base

Materials/Options: Antiqued bronze nesting bird ring, Plated silver nesting bird ring or Plated silver nest ring.

name: Little Reindeer with Christmas Sweater
description:
Christmas sweaters have never looked so good!

This little reindeer is adorned with his best bow tie and christmas sweater for you to wear proudly!

A laser woodcut reindeer brooch to make your Christmas festive! The perfect secret santa gift, stocking stuffer or your way of spreading the Christmas spirit this season (and for many to come!)

Size: 38x69mm 

All the handmade colourful woodcuts have been treated by waterproof, anti-oxidation and scratch-resistant process, so the quality & condition are of a high standard.

name: Nest Brooch
description:
Sweet and Unique.

This hand wrapped nest brooch nurtures these three 'eggs' and adds a beautiful focal point to your outfit. The nest sits in a silver plated base with a pin to adhere it to your outfit.

A great gift for yourself or a loved one! (Especially for those who are nurturing three of their own!)

Size: 20mm, 6mm czech glass beads

Materials: Silver plated base, czech glass beads,  20 gauge wire non tarnish silver plated

name: Winter Branch Earrings
description:
Intricate and elegant.

This beautiful pair of rhodium branches, embellished with czech glass beads will add an intricate element to your attire.

Slipping seamlessly from work wear to evening wear, they are suitably elegant for a range of occasions.

name: Stark Black Circular Earrings
description:
Modern and Bold.

These stark black earrings have a modern circular design and would make a beautiful, elegant addition to your outfit.

Dimension: 38mm

name: Elegant Reindeer Earrings
description:
Merry Christmas!

Who says you need to wear tacky Christmas earrings this year?

Instead you could hold your head high with these contemporary, black and white silhouette reindeer earrings.

Pendant size: 25x18mm

Materials: Resin, antiqued bronze base and antiqued bronze earring hook.

name: Christmas Wreath Earrings
description:
Festive Fun.

These hand wrapped Christmas wreath's, adorned with a bright red bow will put the cheer right into Christmas this year!

A fantastic way to be festive or to play Secret Santa.

Go on, put a pair in a stocking today.

name: Deer Woodcut Brooch
description:
Merry Christmas!

This lovely reindeer brooch is the perfect way to look festive, yet elegant this year. A beautiful laser cut, wooden brooch that displays one of santa's reindeer's mid flight.

The perfect secret santa, stocking stuffer or christmas gift, which can be worn with pride for years to come!

Size: 70x30 mm

name: Reindeer Earrings
description:
Merry Christmas!

Who says you need to wear tacky Christmas earrings this year?

Instead you could hold your head high with these contemporary, black and white silhouette reindeer earrings.

Pendant size: 25x18mm

Materials: Resin, antiqued bronze base and antiqued bronze earring hook.

name: Miniature Babushka Earrings
description:
Cute and Fun.

What great company a pair of Babushka/Matyroshka dolls can make!

Cute front and back these earrings will brighten up your day and add some cute quirkiness to your outfit.

Size: 8x17mm plus earring hooks

Materials: Tibetan silver

name: Mod Bird Lariat
description:
Elegant and Modern.

This modern design depicts a little mod bird fed through a branch to lay beautifully on the chest. Finished with a simple toggle clasp this choice creates a beautiful modern lariat.

Rhodium plated, they are a matte finish and truly elegant.

Size: Bird  16x11 mm, branch 19 x 40mm

Materials: Matte finish rhodium, silver plated chain.

name: Red Patterned Earrings
description:
Modern and Unique.

These funky odd patterned earrings share the same gorgeous red hue and sharp lines, but are both unique. 
A lovely combination for those of us who don't always like to match!

Accentuated with red glass beads and with a base measuring in at 20mm these earrings would make a great addition to your accessories.

name: Two Peas in a Pod
description:
Sweet and Unique.

Share a strong bond with someone? Too grown up for a friendship necklace? These earrings share a similar sentiment but are tasteful and unique.

These earrings can also be appreciated for their pure aesthetic quality - without the narrative. Silver wire wrapped and attached to silver earring hooks, they are elegant and striking.

*Please note the modelled image features the three peas in a pod option as a reference only.

name: Silverware Tea Party
description:
Quirky and Cute.

This miniature tea cup and saucer along with it's tea pot is a gorgeous little combo to add a little quirk to your day!

Great for a mad hatters party or just so you're assured that morning tea is never far away!

name: Christmas Vintage Bow Earrings
description:
'Tis the season!

These festive vintage, Christmas bow earrings add a bit of Christmas cheer to your season, without adding tackiness!

A great gift for a secret santa or for yourself this Christmas season!

Size: 25mm pendant

Materials: Resin, Antiqued bronze over a brass base.

name: Bead and Branch Earrings
description:
Classy and Sweet.

These beautiful matte finish rhodium branches dangle from the end of three glass beads. 

I created this pair of earring to match with a range of necklaces I also make, if you would like to see matching combinations of the necklaces please see the Gunmetal and Mini Mod Bird or the Mod Bird Lariat.

I hope you like this subtle and beautiful combination.
The branch measures 12 x 22 mm, the smoky beads 3mm and the clear glass bead  6mm.

name: Red and Gold Chiyogami Earrings
description:
Eye Catching and Unique.

These drop earrings are inspired by a Japanese paper design, so they are eye catching and have gorgeous clarity of colour.

A unique and trendy conversation point, to add a little touch of something special to your outfit.

Please note: Earrings will be cut from the same piece of Chiyogami paper but the line work may vary slightly as each pair is handmade.

Size: 15mm

Materials: Glass, antiqued bronze, japanese chiyogami paper
